data.description: Great location in the heart of Lakeside with views of Flathead Lake very private with nice matures trees. Remodeled in about 2019. Is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath + bonus room manufactured home on a permanent foundation. Granite bathroom countertops, concrete kitchen countertops, double pane windows throughout, large deck on three sides. Detached 2 car garage plus nice storage shed all on 0.57. Only minute's to Flathead Lake and BlackTail ski Resort. MOTIVATED SELLER,will include Four-Wheeler and snowplow in the sale. Call Cindy Lanier at 406 250-5273 or your real estate professional.
